  <?dbhtml filename="multi_c_rehash.html"?>

  <title>multi_c_rehash-&multi_c_rehash-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      multi_c_rehash scans directories and takes a hash value of each .pem and
      .crt file in the directory. It then creates symbolic links for each of
      the files named by the hash value. This is useful as many programs
      require directories to be set up like this in order to find the
      certificates they require.
    </para>

