  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      Install the package with the following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>sed 's|/usr/local/ssl/certs|/etc/ssl/certs|' -i multi_c_rehash.c &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make -j1 prefix=/usr install</userinput></screen>

